{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/EN-QR.png?t=1737495048\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/T_UI_Settings_Paper_Base_copy.png?t=1737495048\" /><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Flawless Abbey</strong> is a vibrant adventure inside a <i>dream-tower</i>, blending horror, hand-drawn art, and a deeply emotional story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a dreamseeker, and this is just another day on the job. What\u2019s in store this time? A vast, revolving tower that moves and breathes in rhythm with a haunting lullaby?  <br> <br>Your mission is to reach the top and change the abbess's mind. Otherwise, this dream will never end. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>You do want to wake up again, don\u2019t you?</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/box.gif?t=1737495048\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/new_features.png?t=1737495048\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-painted watercolor illustrations crafted by the abbess herself </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intricate musical mechanisms, because the tower <i>is</i> a giant music box</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Corporate benefits and health insurance (psychotherapy not included)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your own dream capsule</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The beast - it\u2019s trying to tear down the tower, and it\u2019s doing a good job of it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A personal assistant who will guide you through the dream, though he\u2019s just as terrified as you are</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A star key - without it, you\u2019ll never reach the top of the tower</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Other dreamseekers. They shouldn\u2019t be here; something isn\u2019t right</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free theater tickets</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/guards2.gif?t=1737495048\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737495048","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/page.bg.jpg?t=1737495048","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/ef47295ca98a6031aac8270004f987e422e8a77d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737495048","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/ef47295ca98a6031aac8270004f987e422e8a77d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737495048","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":1911130,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/EN-QR.png?t=1737495048\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575790/extras/T_UI_Settings_Paper_Base_copy.png?t=1737495048\" /><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Flawless Abbey</strong> is a vibrant adventure inside a <i>dream-tower</i>, blending horror, hand-drawn art, and a deeply emotional stor